des: The greatest hits are on Seacoast Oldies! Serving the seacoast of NH and southern Maine with all the music we grew up with. From artists like The Beatles, Supremes and CCR in the 60’s, to Elton John, Billy Joel and Fleetwood Mac in the 70’s, to Huey Lewis and Hall & Oates in the 80’s, there’s always a lot of variety with less interruption.
